description.narrative: Growing commitment to ECD at the national and local level and increased professional and institutional capacities for ECD across sectors have been achieved over recent years. This has resulted in leverage of resources for scaling up ECD packages at the local level and set the foundation for modelling cross-sectoral ECD and ECI services, capitalizing on evidence-based innovative solutions for the most vulnerable parents and young children and high-quality sustainable learning opportunities for professionals. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:19/12/2019
